Self-hosted web fonts — license note
=====================================

All fonts in this folder are open-licensed under the SIL Open Font License 1.1
(OFL-1.1), which permits embedding, self-hosting, and redistribution. No
proprietary fonts are used. No external/CDN font requests are made at runtime —
every face below is served from this repository's own GitHub Pages origin.

Files & sources
---------------
fraunces.woff2, fraunces-italic.woff2
  Fraunces (variable, weight axis) — Undercase Type / Phaedra Charles & Flavia Zimbardi
  SIL Open Font License 1.1
  https://github.com/undercasetype/Fraunces

jetbrains-mono-400.woff2, jetbrains-mono-700.woff2
  JetBrains Mono — JetBrains s.r.o.
  SIL Open Font License 1.1
  https://github.com/JetBrains/JetBrainsMono

ibm-plex-sans-thai-400.woff2, ibm-plex-sans-thai-600.woff2
  IBM Plex Sans Thai — IBM / Bold Monday
  SIL Open Font License 1.1
  https://github.com/IBM/plex

woff2 binaries were retrieved from the Fontsource distribution
(https://fontsource.org), which redistributes the upstream OFL fonts unmodified.

Full OFL-1.1 text: https://openfontlicense.org
